¿PAUL DOUGLAS PLANT
8.10.1954 - 9.1.2021
Our Wonderful Husband, Dad and Grandpa.
We miss you and love you so very much.
A beautiful spot to sit and chat to you Paul."©
ÁIn Loving Memory of
DESRIE DENISE GREENHOUSE
Passed Away Peacefully 28th January 2022
Sadly Missed by Husband John and Family
Always in Our Thoughts
'The Lady from the Chemist'"╝
╣Our beautiful Sister, Wife and Mother
Beryl Shaw,
We will keep you safe in our hearts
and love you forever

To our wonderful sister Joan Baird
and her son David -
not a day goes by that you are not missed
or loved by us all.
Forever in our thoughts.

Out lovely Sister Margaret Davies, Always in our
thoughts, not a day goes by that you are not loved or 
missed by all the family, Loving and Caring mother to all
her children and grandchildren

Our beloved brother
Brian Pennicott,
You will always be loved and never forgotten.
Forever in our hearts."Ì
█Hayley Marie Johnston
28.07.1969 - 25.11.2022
Our minds still talk to you, our hearts still look for you
But our souls know you're at peace
We miss you so much every single day
Love Always
Your Family & Friends xx"¶
